  "texts": [
    "We observed that human judgments align with our quantitative evaluation.",
    "Yet, humans still prefer human-written stories over model-generated ones, which suggests that capturing coherence, visual grounding, and non-repetitiveness may not (yet) be the whole story.",
    "The human evaluation analysis we performed is arguably small-scale.",
    "As such, we cannot rule out that carrying it out with more annotators and a larger set of stimuli may lead to different patterns of results.",
    "Second, the of models we experimented with is quite limited, which is an obvious limitation of this work."
